                            <enum>(ii)</enum>
 <text>by adding at the end the following:</text> <quoted-block style="OLC" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id6fb272dcf151412fae6f736c45008a01"> <subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id56403cda6f8b40958484e7867c82ad90" indent="up1"> <enum>(B)</enum> <text>Notwithstanding subparagraph (A), the Administration may not assess or collect any ongoing guarantee fee under subparagraph (A) with respect to a loan guaranteed under this title if the loan is made—</text>
                                    <clause commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id397c6650bacf4965a482bbfa4a40a22e">
