 <text>in subsection (i)—</text> <clause commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="iddb9f94fcaba847989f0bc716272a4871"> <enum>(i)</enum> <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by striking <quote><header-in-text style="OLC" level="subsection">Two-Year Waiver of Fees</header-in-text>—The</quote> and inserting the following: “<header-in-text style="OLC" level="section">Waiver of Fees</header-in-text>.—</text>
