 <text>by striking <quote>and</quote> at the end.</text> </subclause> </clause> </subparagraph> </paragraph> </subsection> </section> <section commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id9b060b18db234c7688913f1cf6ac70af"> <enum>4.</enum> <header>Equity injection</header> <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id9595850a30a247edaab6381b4e311215"> <enum>(a)</enum> <header>Small Business Act</header> <text>Section 7(a) of the Small Business Act (<external-xref legal-doc="usc" parsable-cite="usc/15/636">15 U.S.C. 636(a)</external-xref>) is amended by adding at the end the following:</text>
